    @SupportedAnnotationTypes(value="com.google.appengine.spi.ServiceProvider")
@SupportedSourceVersion(value=RELEASE_6)
@SupportedOptions(value={"debug","verify"})
public class ServiceProviderProcessor
extends javax.annotation.processing.AbstractProcessor
    Processes ServiceProvider annotations and generates the service provider configuration files described in ServiceLoader.

    Processor Options:

    • debug - turns on debug statements
